Package: qkit
Title: A Small Set of Useful Quarto Templates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gabriel", "Cabrera Guzmán",
           email = "gabriel.cabrera.guz@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8803-2338"))
Description: A small set of Quarto project templates with RStudio
    integration: Beamer presentations, academic CVs, Quarto book projects
    (Krantz document class), and minimalist economics/finance papers
    (with a separate Internet Appendix). Includes custom LaTeX styling,
    enhanced author/affiliation support with ORCID, a Pandoc Lua filter
    for markdown-first CV authoring, and helper functions for rendering.
